content: I'm willing to give it a try. I'll set my bedtime 15 minutes earlier and see how it goes. By the way, I've been trying to establish a consistent wake-up time for weeks now, and I used to wake up at 8:30 am on weekdays, but since I started my new job three weeks ago, I've been waking up at 7:15 am to have enough time to get ready and catch the bus at 8:00 am.
